{"id": "1004334", "question": "plt.imshow显示的黑白图片颜色很奇怪", "description": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10\"><p>我加载的是MNIST数据，按道理是黑白的手写数字，结果显示出来是彩色的</p><pre><code class=\"python\">plt.imshow(train_images[0])\r\nplt.show()</code></pre><p><img data-filename=\"keras5 (1).png\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"width: 255px;\"/><br/></p><p>请问该怎么调整？</p></div>", "viewer": 5729, "tags": ["统计/机器学习", "计算机视觉", "数据可视化", "Python"], "answers": [{"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>设置一下cmap</p><pre><code class=\"python\">plt.imshow(train_images[0], cmap='binary')</code></pre><p>或者</p><pre><code class=\"python\">plt.imshow(train_images[0], cmap='Greys_r')</code></pre><p>或者</p><pre><code class=\"python\">plt.imshow(train_images[0], cmap='Greys')</code></pre></div>", "lvl2_answer": ["嗯～试了下，这三个方法都可行，谢谢～"]}]}